         <div type="translation">
            <p>
               <choice corresp="#a1 #a2 #a3 #a4 #a5 #a6 #b1 #b2 #b3 #b4 #b5 #b6">
                  <seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:schmidtkt2001"/><citedRange>325</citedRange></bibl></seg>
                  <seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:broomhead1962"/><citedRange>213</citedRange></bibl></seg>
               </choice>
               <choice corresp="#a2">
                  <seg><seg type="prim_transl">I will let rain a rain of weapons on the earth, and with a flood of weapons I will fill the cardinal directions.  (cf 246; 325)</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:peyrot2013b"/><citedRange>670</citedRange></bibl></seg>
               </choice>
               <choice corresp="#a5">
                  <seg><seg type="prim_transl">There is no one in this world who could have brought me into this misfortune by [his] power.</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:peyrot2013b"/><citedRange>340</citedRange></bibl></seg>
               </choice>
               <choice corresp="#a6">
                  <seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:schmidtkt1974"/><citedRange>410 n.2</citedRange></bibl></seg>
                  <seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:peyrot2013b"/><citedRange>339</citedRange></bibl></seg>
               </choice>
               <choice corresp="#b1">
                  <seg><seg type="prim_transl">Die Pfeile eines Rachsüchtigen(?) haben mich heftig (ins Herz) getroffen.</seg><seg type="sec_transl" resp="TI">The arrows of a vengeful(?) one have struck (my heart) violently.</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:schmidtkt1974"/><citedRange>368</citedRange></bibl></seg>
               </choice>
               <choice corresp="#b3">
                  <seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:peyrot2013b"/><citedRange>295</citedRange></bibl></seg>
               </choice>
               <choice corresp="#b3 #B 94 a4">
                  <seg><seg type="prim_transl">For now I will perish with the root.  (cf 326)</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:peyrot2013b"/><citedRange>295</citedRange></bibl></seg>
               </choice>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div type="comments">
            <p>
               <note type="parallels"><ref type="ms" target="txt:m-tht93"/>, <ref type="ms" target="txt:m-tht94"/> and <ref type="ms" target="txt:m-pkns36and20"/></note>
               <note type="remarks">According to <bibl><title corresp="ref:broomhead1962"/><citedRange>213</citedRange></bibl> "[w]ritten in medium ductus, and very clearly preserved, it is the left edge of a six line manuscript. A number in the margin verso is not completely clear and may be either '41' or '71'".
He also identifies this fragment as folios 21-22 (op.cit.).</note>
            </p>
